svg.title: Sheet Music for "Rye Straw (G)"

text.tspan: Notes: Doc's version first, followed by a few variations I've heard.
Note about the chords - this can easily follow a straight G pattern, but I kind of like the
"rocking" pattern between G and C on the A part that I've heard in other versions.
